quran[52]{c,v,t}:
  69,1,"Tẽeg yel-yɩtgã. [ Dĩni yikrã sɩdgre]"
  69,2,"Bõe la dĩni-yikr sɩdgdã?"
  69,3,"La bõe n wilgd foo bõe la sɩdgdã?"
  69,4,"A Ṯamuud la a ʿAad yagsa peleng yɩgsã."
  69,5,"La sã n yaa ne Ṯamuudu, b halka bãmb ne tãs-kεgenga,"
  69,6,"La sã n yaa ne ʿAad, b halka bãmb ne seb-fugdg sẽn yaa kεgenga."
  69,7,"A nom-a-la bãmb zug yʋnd a yopoe la rasem a nii sẽn pʋg taaba. Fo nee nebã a pʋgẽ tɩ b rʋrẽ wala tamar-giisi."
  69,8,"Rẽ yĩnga fo nee b pʋgẽ kεlld bɩ?"
  69,9,"Lɑ ɑ Fɩr-ʿaoon la sẽn reng-b yẽ taoorã la a Mutafɩkaat (b sẽn lebg rãmb n kiblgã) wa ne tʋʋm-beedo."
  69,10,"Tɩ b kɩɩs b Soabã tẽn-tʋʋmã t'A yõk-b kõn-n-põsg yõkre."
  69,11,"Ad Tõndo, koomã sẽn wa n puuga, Tõnd rɩka yãmb yɑɑb-rãmbã koglgã pʋga."
  69,12,"Bʋɩl yĩng tɩ D na maan-a tɩ yaa tẽegr ne yãmba; la na kεlg-a tʋbr sẽn wʋmd gomde."
  69,13,"Tɩ b sã n wa fʋʋs Baorgẽ wã, fʋʋs-vuka."
  69,14,"La b zẽk Tẽngã la saasã n sãeeg-b sãeeg-vuka."
  69,15,"Ra-kãngã, Yɩɩbã yɩtame."
  69,16,"Tɩ saagã pãrg tɩ yẽndã lebg vɑlengɑ ra-kãng rɑɑrã."
  69,17,"Tɩ malεgsã be a kɩremsã. La tʋkda fo Soabã naam-zaoorã b zugu ra-kãngã raare, (malεgs a) nĩi."
  69,18,"Ra-kãng raarã, b ballda yãmba, ned ba a yembr pa solgd yãmb pʋgẽ ye."
  69,19,"La ned ning b sẽn wa n kõ-a a gafo ne a rɩtgo, a yetame: ""reeg-y m gafã n karme"","
  69,20,"""M da tẽeme tɩ mam na n sega m gεεlã."
  69,21,"Tɩ yẽnda be vɩɩm pʋg sẽn yaa yard vɩɩm."
  69,22,"N be Arzãn pʋg sẽn zẽke."
  69,23,"A tɩ-biisã fãsb pẽeme."
  69,24,"Rɩ-y la y yũ, tɩ yaa beelg ne yãmb sẽn dɑ tʋme rasem rãmb sẽn loogã."
  69,25,"La ned ning b sẽn wa n kõ-a a gaf ne a goabga, a yetame: ""b sã n da pa kõ maam m gafã pa são?"
  69,26,"Tɩ m pa bãng m gεεl sẽn ya-a a soaba."
  69,27,"M kũumã sã n da yɩẽ tεk-tεka pa são?"
  69,28,"M arzεk pa naf maam ye!"
  69,29,"Mam pãngã loog n basa maam."
  69,30,"Yõk-y-yã-a n balg-a soɑɑm-dɑgoɑngɑ."
  69,31,"Rẽ poorẽ kẽes-y-yã-a Gεhɩɩma."
  69,32,"Rẽ poorẽ kẽes-y-yã-a bãng pʋgẽ, a woglmã yaa kãntɩɩs pis-yopoe."
  69,33,"A ra yɩɩme n pa kõt sɩd ne Wẽnd sẽn yaa zɩsgr Naabã ye."
  69,34,"A ra pa pirsd ne ninbãan-ned rɩlgr ye."
  69,35,"Rẽnd pa be ne yẽ rũndã raarã zĩ-kãnga, zao ye."
  69,36,"Pa rɩɩb me ye, ralla nod meto."
  69,37,"Pa rɩt-a, sã n pa tʋʋm-beed rãmba."
  69,38,"M na wẽen ne bũmb ning yãmb sẽn ne."
  69,39,"La bũmb ning yãmb sẽn pa ne."
  69,40,"Ad yãoondã (Alkʋrãɑnɑ) yaa Tẽn-tʋʋm sẽn yaa wagell koεεga."
  69,41,"A pa yɩɩl-yɩɩnd koεεg ye, paood yãmb sẽn kõt sɩda."
  69,42,"A leb n pa bag-bʋgd koεεg ye, paood yãmb sẽn tagsde."
  69,43,"Yaa sẽn sig n yi bõn-naandsã Soab nengẽ."
  69,44,"A sã n dag n pas goam-sãnda n roglg Tõnd zugu."
  69,45,"D na yõk-a a poorẽ ne rɩtgo."
  69,46,"Rẽ poorẽ, D na wãag a sũur gĩindi."
  69,47,"Tɩ ned ba a yembr pa be yãmb pʋgẽ sẽn tõe n gɩd Tõnd tɩ D pɑ tɑ-ɑ ye."
  69,48,"La ad yẽnda( Kʋrãɑnɑ) yaa tẽegr ne wẽn-zoεtbã."
  69,49,"La Tõnd miime tɩ be yãmb pʋgẽ sẽn yaa yagsdba."
  69,50,"La yell sẽn yalẽ, a yaa bõn kɩfr-dãmb zugu."
  69,51,"La ad ɑ yaa sɩd vẽenega."
  69,52,"Bɩ f yɩlg f Soab zɩsgã yʋʋre."
